{
 "file": "_STGSP1B.bin",
 "source_size": 25364,
 "built_size": 27479,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1603",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……终于、等到这一刻了啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8e2e87902e826e7d7e7b9efb6e91fe7bae7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x163a",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x166b",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "历经苦难的战斗之后、总算亲手换来的和{00}平……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fbe8b7e9e6e866e7b4ef28e7ffe7cde7fe02e881e889e894ef66ea78efcfe7b4e7d300e8870909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1682",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……可问题在于、人类是否已成长到、足{00}以握住这份和平了呢……",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c4e997ea12ef29e87902efb2e841e7b6e9bbef3ae837ef34e7d702ea1e00e7f3eb37e859e7b9ea22e7d3e887e7bae907090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16cd",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……看来、还是得由我们来教导他们才行{00}呢、德基姆",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f6d902e7f7e7b6e80ae8a68be7bbd9eaacea4be80ce7bbe8369f00e90702e82ce829e823000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x173c",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正是如此、玛莉梅亚大人",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7b6e7f0e7ca02e845e81ee9f2e7d6beb40000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x179d",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……这是父亲大人托付给我的圣诞礼物…{00}…",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b9e7b6e888e894efa5efb2e7f4e97ee839efcce7b4e90ded06eb65e99e0900090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17ba",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "得好好地送到大家手里才行呢",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ae7c7e7c7ef63e9bae7d7efa5e7dfef66ef31e836efd6e9070000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17c9",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵呵……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3def3d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17e8",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "队、队长！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c902e7c9ef34ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1805",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哇啊啊啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea88e7c3e7c3e7c3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x185d",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！这帮家伙、到底是什么来头……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97e7b9e910e7dfe7fd02e7d7e9b4e7b6e7dde7bdefcfe92e0909ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1893",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "无能之辈的时代、已经结束了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dce7c6e7cded0ce7b4ef2de8e702ef3ae8b7e868e895e7baef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1911",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是OZ起兵了吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6ed1ceedae847ef93e7bae802ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1938",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "前OZ的激进派发动了兵变、占领了联邦{00}的主要设施……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef51ed1ceedae7b4e9b9e892e985e870ef30e7baef93e95502eb51ea20e7baef2eefaa00e7b4e954ef2aeb43eb8d0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1956",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……情报部竟然连一点征兆都没察觉、完{00}全是被人摆了一道",
   "zh_hex": "150909e88be913ccef2ce7efe86e87e822ecd2eddde840e7d8ea8be8ae02e87e00bbe7b6e7f1b4eb8be7ba87e82a000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1991",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、我们预防者该……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02efcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee8980909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19bc",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "目前、情报部正在收集有关叛军的情报",
   "zh_hex": "15d5ba02e88be913ccef3bef29e926ea98e7cbe8bbef43e7e0e7b4e88be91300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19d8",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一旦查明主谋的位置……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6ebcdeae9ef39e954ea6ee7b4e834ea0e09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a19",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "舰、舰长！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d402e7d4ef34ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a3e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7baef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a62",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这就投到屏幕上！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7c5e948e7d7ed4eec14ef4cef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a88",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我乃世界国家元首的正统继承人、玛莉梅{00}亚·克休里那达……",
   "zh_hex": "158befdde83ce8f5a1e7dfecaeef40e7b4ef3be929e9d6ea75b402e845e81ee9f200e7d604e7d5e90eef31e7b7ef2b090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aa4",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也就是特列斯·克休里那达之女",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7c5e7b6e7cfe8b5e7c8ef4be7d5e90eef31e7b7ef2be7cdefad00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ab5",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我要继承父亲的遗志、人唯有不断战{00}斗、才是有意义的存在！",
   "zh_hex": "150909efccef2ae9d6ea75e888e894e7b4eba9ea1802efb2ea89e7cbe7b5e982ef2800e7ff02e836e7b6e7cbef3ce8cee7b4e993ef29ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1af2",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "特列斯·克休里那达的女儿吗……这下又{00}冒出个了不得的人物啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cfe8b5e7c8ef4be7d5e90eef31e7b7ef2be7b4efadeb7ce8020909e7b9ef4de8f100eb7fefbee828e7bae7b5e80ae7b4efb2e99ee7c3000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b2a",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b4e",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……看来事态相当严重呢",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f6efcfefb8e994e8b1ef53eaa1e8a1e907000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b79",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……面对突如其来的兵变、正规军光是重{00}整阵脚就已忙得不可开交",
   "zh_hex": "150909e862e7bee8b6e7f0e8cfefcfe7b4ef93e95502ef3bea42e7e0e83de7b6e8a100e9feeb48eb68e7c5ef3aea06e80ae7b5e7c4e7fae8610000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bb1",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么说来、又要用到我们的力量了呢",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bde7edd902e8f1ef2ad8e7d78be7bbe7b4dae851e7bae907000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1be4",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "凭刚才那段通讯、叛军主力的位置不久也{00}会查明",
   "zh_hex": "15ea49e8bce836e7b7ea6bef59eb1b02ef43e7e0e954efb0e7b4e834ea0ee7b5e9dbe7c000e7e2eae9ef3900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c00",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "希望你们能向敌方中枢挺进、阻止事态进{00}一步扩大……",
   "zh_hex": "15e87be965e7b8e7bbe7c6efc1e7e3efb1ef4eec75eb5ce89202e8efe869efb8e994e89200efb6ea93ec1aefa509090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c3e",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不、已经没有慢慢来的工夫了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b502ef3ae8b7e7d8e7cbe979e979efcfe7b4eae4e830e7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c70",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "巴尔特菲尔德先生？",
   "zh_hex": "15e85be7e1e7cfea6ce7e1e82cef8bef8d050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cc4",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一支所属不明的MS部队、正在接近！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e883e7fbea24e7b5ef39e7b4efa7ef9eef70e7c902ef3bef29efceefd8ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cf0",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d12",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌人也没蠢到、会放着我们这支游击战力{00}不管",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb2e7c0e7d8e94be7d702e7e2e86ce86defcce7bbe7b9e883ea94e7ccef28efb000e7b5e93b0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d41",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……拉米亚斯舰长！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef34ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d66",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯！",
   "zh_hex": "15e865ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d76",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全舰、转入攻击态势！！迎击敌方MS！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e7d402e9c2e891ef67e7cce994e8fdef97ef97e931e7cce7e3efb1efa7ef9eef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1da7",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就是叛军吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7b6ef43e7e0e80209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dd7",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全员、立即进入迎击态势！预防者全舰、{00}开始战斗！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e84902e86be855e892e891e931e7cce994e8fdef97ea5ae968ef6eefb4e7d40200e7fae908ef28e7ffef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e19",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！预防者的实力、竟有这么强！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef97ea5ae968ef6ee7b4e87fefb002ef2ce7cbe7b9e7bde8adef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e2e",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "事到如今、再也不能保留战力了！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb8e7d7e7f0efb902e80be7c0e7b5e7c6ea47e98cef28efb0e7baef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e47",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "出动那支部队！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efbeef30e7b7e883ef70e7c9ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e86",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b60909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ec2",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "大意了……！",
   "zh_hex": "15efa5ef3ce7ba0909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ecd",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "毕竟是前OZ、原来和蓝色宇宙也有勾结{00}吗！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea2cef2ce7b6baed1ceeda02e8e4d9e7d3eaf1e89fe8bee8bfe7c0e7cbecb7e86800e8020600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f18",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好！就这样一口气、把预防者……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7ef97e7c5e7b9e7daefb6eabde8ed02e81bea5ae968ef6e09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f50",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f89",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "既然特列斯的亡灵已经现身……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c4e7efe7cfe8b5e7c8e7b4ebb2eaebef3ae8b7e82fe88d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fa9",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我可没法乖乖地、就此长眠不起啊",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c4e7d8e84ee9a3e9a3ef6302e7c5e7caef34ed8fe7b5e847e7c3000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fe8",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您就是预防者的玛琉·拉米亚斯舰长吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7c5e7b6ea5ae968ef6ee7b4e845ead2ef4be7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef34e7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2016",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、您是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e835e7b60909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x203b",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "说到底、我也不过是一阵灭火之风罢了…{00}…",
   "zh_hex": "15e7ede7d7e9b402efcce7c0e7b5ef36e7b6efb6eb48e8e1e8dae7cdeb75eaefe7ba09000900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x204a",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就请允许我、自称为预防者·风吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e83aecade8a7efcc02efb5ea01e7c1ea5ae968ef6eef4beb75e7d00000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2080",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "预防者……风……？",
   "zh_hex": "15ea5ae968ef6e0909eb750909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20a8",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "作为一名渴望完全和平的士兵、就让我来{00}助你们一臂之力！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2fe7c1efb6e8aced84e965e87eefb4e7d3e887e7b4ef64ef9302e7c5e7f9efccefcf00ea23e7b8e7bbefb6ee92e7cdefb0ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20ec",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "杰克斯……您果然还活着、我一直都坚信{00}着",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ebe7d5e7c80909e835e871e7efe7f7e8d4e86d02efccefb6e875e840eb80e90f00e86d000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2121",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是诺茵吗、又要让你为我操劳了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e972e971e80202e8f1ef2ae7f9e7b8e7c1efcceac7ec4ae7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x214f",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我再也不会离开您的身边了",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce80be7c0e7b5e7e2e901e7fae835e7b4e88de899e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2160",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我一直、一直在等着您、再也不想这样等{00}下去了",
   "zh_hex": "15efccefb6e87502efb6e875ef29e826e86de83502e80be7c0e7b5e7e6e7b9e7dae82600ef4de7ebe7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2196",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你真的愿意吗……跟着我这样的人？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e820e7b4e961ef3ce8020909e973e86defcce7b9e7dae7b4efb205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21c0",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正因为是这样的您……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3bef33e7c1e7b6e7b9e7dae7b4e8350909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21e8",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x220b",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、我们走吧、诺茵！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02efcce7bbe890e7d002e972e971ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2238",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好的、杰克斯！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e7b402e8ebe7d5e7c8ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2266",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……似乎已经结束了呢",
   "zh_hex": "150909e944e933ef3ae8b7e868e895e7bae9070000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2299",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟然连预防者都已被暗中下了手……真不{00}是个好对付的对手啊",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7efe86eea5ae968ef6ee840ef3ae7f1ea6aef4eef4de7baef660909e820e7b500e7b6e828e7c7e7bee97ee7b4e7beef66e7c30000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22e2",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "玛莉梅亚……",
   "zh_hex": "15e845e81ee9f2e7d609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22e9",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟是特列斯大人的千金……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7b6e7cfe8b5e7c8efa5efb2e7b4eafde902090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22f9",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2319",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "封锁第一道门！",
   "zh_hex": "15eb83ebfae94087e82ae90c0600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x233e",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "接着封锁第二到第六道门！",
   "zh_hex": "15b7e86deb83ebfae940ea13e7d7e940eddfe82ae90c060000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23ae",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23f7",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不觉得奇怪吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5e8aee80ae904ea07e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2406",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在一个没有兵器的和平世界里、为何还需{00}要这样的避难所呢？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb6e828e7d8e7cbef93e8c3e7b4e7d3e887e83ce8f5ef3102e7c1efbce7f7e92d00ef2ae7b9e7dae7b4efd9e866e7fbe9070500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2441",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2465",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若要打个比方、历史就如同一曲永不停歇{00}的华尔兹",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7ef2ae7f5e828e825d002e8fbe925e7c5e7f0e85d87ece2e9bfe7b5e934ee4500e7b4ed2ce7e1e8560000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2487",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "战争、和平、革命这三拍子、将永无止境{00}地周而复始……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28e85202e7d3e88702edc5e853e7b9eaa0e804e88602e84ae9bfe7dce869eb8100bfea5ce89ce9eee908090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24be",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你究竟想做什么？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e906ef2ce7e6e81ce7dde7bd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24eb",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "让他们、统统向我下跪",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f9e80ce7bb02e929e929efc1efccef4deff30000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24fa",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……这世上所有的人类",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b9e83cef4ce7fbe7cbe7b4efb2e84100000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2520",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2541",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没错、随着我的登基、人类将迎来一个全{00}新的时代",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e88502e9a1e86defcce7b4e9a0e82902efb2e841e84ae931efcfefb6e828efb400ef8ae7b4ef2de8e7000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2561",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "莉莉娜·匹斯克拉福特、就请你来协助我{00}完成这件事",
   "zh_hex": "15e81ee81ee7eaef4bed2ae7c8e7d5e7c2ea7ce7cf02e7c5e83ae7b8efcfe8f6ea23efcc00e87ee837e7b9e991efb8000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2599",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……协助？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8f6ea23050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25bd",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你身为前桑克王国的女王、如今又是现任{00}次官……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e88de7c1ef51ea2be7d5e884efc4e7b4efade88402e7f0efb9e8f1e7b6e82fe89a00e864ef920909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25d6",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一度还在迪尔麦优的扶持下、出任过{00}世界国家的代表……",
   "zh_hex": "1587e96de7f7ef29ea11e7e1ec43e9afe7b4eecee9ef8902afe89aef3600e83ce8f5a1e7dfe7b4e8e7e9e709090000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25f8",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就由你以世界代表的身份、把地球圈的最{00}高之位托付给我",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e8a6e7b8e7f3e83ce8f5e8e7e9e7e7b4e88dea2202e81bef63efd3e9fbe7b4e8c500e812e7cde834e7f4e97ee839efcc000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2637",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你抓我来、就是为了这个……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e962efccefcf02e7c5e7b6e7c1e7bae7b9e82809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x265c",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵呵……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3def3d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2663",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你手中的权限、远比你自己所想的、拥有{00}更强的影响力",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8aec0e7b4eb39eb2302e94ce825e7b8abe8c9e7fbe7e6e7b402eb35e7cb00e952e8ade7b4ea8eecbfda0000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x269f",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "布鲁塞尔总统府……",
   "zh_hex": "15e831e8a2e950e7e1e881e929ea6009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26c5",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "根据目前查明的情报、玛莉梅亚·克休里{00}那达她……",
   "zh_hex": "15e9b8e8ccd5baeae9ef39e7b4e88be91302e845e81ee9f2e7d604e7d5e90eef3100e7b7ef2be88e090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26dd",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正和多利安次官一起、躲在总统府的避难{00}所里",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7d3e7e9e82ee7fce8648f87e84702ea6fef29e881e929ea60e7b4cae86600e7fbef3100000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2717",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x273b",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "四周被OZ的MS团团围住、守得水泄不{00}通……",
   "zh_hex": "15eb52ea5ce7f1ed1ceedae7b4efa7ef9eea5eea5ee9dee85902e8a8e80aebd4ed7ee7b500ef590909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2759",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "况且、正规军正手忙脚乱地应对、根本动{00}弹不得",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d0e99902ef3bea42e7e0ef3bef66ea06eb68e976ef63e873e7be02e9b8efa6ef3000e946e7b5e80a00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x278f",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "眼下能够行动的、恐怕除了你们之外再无{00}他人了",
   "zh_hex": "15e90bef4de7c6e920efd6ef30e7b402eb33e958e974e7bae7b8e7bbe7cde8f7e80be7dc00e80cefb2e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27c7",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27d0",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也就是击破玛莉梅亚军的中枢、并救出多{00}利安次官、对吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7c5e7b6e7ccc7e845e81ee9f2e7d6e7e0e7b4c0ec7502e957e8caafe7e900e82ee7fce8648f02e7bee7d00000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27ec",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……任务、我明白了、我们这就赶往现场",
   "zh_hex": "150909e89ae94f02efccef39e809e7ba02efcce7bbe7b9e7c5ea04e911e82fe8760000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2827",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我也知道这是项危险的任务、可如今、你{00}们就是我们唯一的指望了",
   "zh_hex": "158be7c0e85ae82ae7b9e7b6eec5e935e932e7b4e89ae94f02e7c4e7f0a202e7b800e7bbe7c5e7b68be7bbea8987e7b4e8c0e965e7ba00000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x284b",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……拜托你们了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e91ae7f4e7b8e7bbe7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x286c",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "舰长！前进航线上出现雷达反应！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d4ef3406bae892e9c1e916b2afe82fe8afef2be87ce8730606000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x287e",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是扎夫特的战舰！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e84be830e7cfe7b4ef28e7d4ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28a5",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你说扎夫特！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8e7ede84be830e7cfef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28c9",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是要协助我们……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ef2ae8f6ea23efcce7bb0909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28f0",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28f7",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对于这次OZ残党军的兵变、{00}我们PLANT也深感忧虑",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee879e7b9e864ed1ceedae97bea73e7e0e7b4cee95502008be7bbeed4e81aea9ceed3eed6e7c0eb0de87dee1deba10000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2915",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可以的话、扎夫特也想出兵协助、设法收{00}拾这个局面、可是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7f3e7b4e81f02e84be830e7cfe7c0e7e6efbeef93e8f6ea2302eb43e84ee92600eae6e7b9e828ea8ce86202e7c4e7b6090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2937",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "碍于与联邦之间的条约、我们无法自由调{00}动军队",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c6e879e832ef2eefaae7cde8fce7b4e9d4e9ac02efcce7bbe7dce84eefb5e8a6e95c00ef30e7e0e7c900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x297a",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、是要支援我们吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f302e7b6ef2ae883e863efcce7bbe80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29a4",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "ZGMF-X23S、救世主高达……是{00}我们扎夫特的最新锐机体",
   "zh_hex": "15eedaeed1efa7eca5ef71eed9ef5fef60ef9e02e8cae83ce954e812ef2b0909e7b600efcce7bbe84be830e7cfe7b4e8c5ef8aed14e7e4ef4f000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29c3",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们希望、能把它提供给你们预防者",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe87be96502e7c6e81be978e821eca9e839e7b8e7bbea5ae968ef6e0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29fb",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "扎夫特的最新锐机、要给我们？",
   "zh_hex": "15e84be830e7cfe7b4e8c5ef8aed14e7e402ef2ae839efcce7bb050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a26",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "迪兰达尔议长下过指示、要我们尽一切可{00}能支援贵舰",
   "zh_hex": "15ea11e86fef2be7e1e8e3ef3489ef36e8c0eab002ef2a8be7bbe8f287ef3fe7c400e7c6e883e863e930e7d4000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a67",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔、可是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d02e7c4e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a8b",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那台MS、就叫救世主高达是吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7ea16efa7ef9e02e7c5e8c1e8cae83ce954e812ef2be7b6e7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2abc",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……舰长？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d4ef34050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ae1",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如今正是分秒必争的关头、克瓦特罗大尉",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0efb9ef3be7b6efaeee79e860e852e7b4e8bbe92e02e7d5e99fe7cfe7ecefa5efc60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2af5",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再说、战力哪怕多上一分、也能让人更安{00}心",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7ed02ef28efb0e8ffe958e7e9ef4cefb6efae02e7c0e7c6e7f9efb2e952e7fc00e82d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b2a",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b4c",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "迪兰达尔议长的这份好意、我们就感激地{00}收下了",
   "zh_hex": "15ea11e86fef2be7e1e8e3ef34e7b4e7b9ea22e7c7ef3c028be7bbe7c5e87de9b9bf00e92689e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5bda",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟、竟然就到此为止了……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2c02ef2ce7efe7c5e7d7e7cae7c1e869e7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c66",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这一路征战、辛苦你了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9efb6e8d2ecd2ef2802ea58e9e6e7b8e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c73",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你将这条『宇宙世纪路线』一路游玩{00}到了最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b8e84ae7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb6e8d2ea94e97000e7d7e7bae8c5e7fe000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c93",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的征战、就先在此告{00}一段落了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ecd2ef2802e7c5ef8bef29e7cae8e500efb6ea6be92ae7ba0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5cb2",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续下去、今后也请你{00}继续尽情游玩",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9adef4de7eb02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b800e9d6e9ade8f2e88bea94e97000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5cd7",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、为一路通关本路线的你、还特意准{00}备了一个特别关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702e7c1efb6e8d2ef59e8bbefa6e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7e7cfef3ce87a00e877e7baefb6e828e7cfe7e5e8bbe8010000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5cfe",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头作战至今的大天使队之间{00}的特别演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e832efcce7bbefaee92eef2fef28e897efb9e7b4efa5e844e83fe7c9e7cde8fc00e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d1f",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和他们交手一番、亲自检验你培养至今的{00}部队实力、也是件好事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3e80ce7bbe861ef66efb6ee6d02e894efb5ee40ea99e7b8edfeec0be897efb9e7b400ef70e7c9e87fefb002e7c0e7b6e991e7c7efb80000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d44",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特殊演习』、便能与{00}他们一决高下",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfed7bea2feab60d02e8fae7c6e83200e80ce7bbefb6e8abe812ef4d00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d69",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请继续游玩『SD高达G世{00}代DS』吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae9d6e9adea94e9700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83c00e8e7ef96ef9e0de7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d8d",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也希望你能静下心来、尽情玩到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e87be965e7b8e7c6eab3ef4de82defcf02e8f2e88be970e7d7e8c5e7fe00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e06",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你一路以来、一直陪着我这个不太靠{00}得住的舰长",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b8efb6e8d2e7f3efcf02efb6e875ef42e86defcce7b9e828e7b5e86ae8c700e80ae859e7b4e7d4ef3400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e25",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』、就到此告一段落{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae8e5efb6ea6be92a00e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e43",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说、我们预防者的这场战斗、是已经结{00}束了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ed02efcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4e7b9e876ef28e7ff02e7b6ef3ae8b7e86800e895e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e5d",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不过游戏本身也还能继续下去哦、今{00}后也请你继续享受游戏吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88de7c0e7f7e7c6e9d6e9adef4de7ebe91902efb900e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e9d6e9adec06e8c8ea94ea3ee7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e83",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为一路玩通这条路线的你、还另外准备了{00}全新的关卡哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1efb6e8d2e970ef59e7b9e9d4e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7e99be8f7e87ae877e7ba00efb4ef8ae7b4e8bbe801e9190000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ea7",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头、和提坦斯及新吉翁交过{00}手的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e8328be7bbcde92e02e7d3e821e843e7c8e9cfef8ae7d9ee88e861ef3600aee7b40909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ec2",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……正是和那支隆德·贝尔队之间的特别{00}演习哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef3be7b6e7d3e7b7e883ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7cde8fce7b4e7cfe7e500ea2feab6e9190000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ed5",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能和{00}他们一战了哦",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e7d300e80ce7bbefb6ef28e7bae9190000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5efb",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请你一定要去挑战看看哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae7b8efb6e867ef2ae7ebeae7ef28e7f6e7f6e9190000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5f09",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请继续游玩『SD高达G世{00}代DS』吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae9d6e9adea94e9700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83c00e8e7ef96ef9e0de7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5f2d",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自由对战的战火！尽情冲杀吧、大天使{00}号！！』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5e8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97e8f2e88be95ee89be7d002efa5e844e83f00e833ef97ef970d000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5fae",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号的舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露{00}中佐",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7b4e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e85800ef4eefba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5fbe",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、请允许我向你一路以来的出色指挥{00}致以由衷的敬意",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802e83aecade8a78b9de7b887e8d2e7f3d9e7b4afe89fe8c0e94900ea32e7f3e8a6edb3e7b4ee38ef3c00000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5fe0",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正是多亏了你的协助、我们才终于得以奋{00}战到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7b6e7e9eab7e7bae7b8e7b4e8f6ea2302efcce7bbe836e8e2e879e80ae7f3ef4600ef28e7d7e8c5e7fe000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6002",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』、就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6018",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说、我们主天使队的这场战斗、是已经{00}到此结束了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ed02efcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4e7b9e876ef28e7ff02e7b6ef3ae8b700e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6031",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续下去、今后也请你{00}继续尽情游玩",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9adef4de7eb02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b800e9d6e9ade8f2e88bea94e970000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6055",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战今后仍可继续下去、另外、只要{00}选择『特别演习』……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28efb9e7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9adef4de7eb02e99be8f702ef32ef2a00e966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6080",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "便能与隆德·贝尔、预防者一同进行一场{00}联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fae7c6e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e102ea5ae968ef6eefb6e85de892efd6efb6e87600ef2eefc0ea2feab6000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x609e",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我坚信、以你的本领、在与他们的战斗中{00}也定能克敌制胜",
   "zh_hex": "15efcceb80e90f02e7f3e7b8e7b4efa6ea2002ef29e832e80ce7bbe7b4ef28e7ffef4e00e7c0e867e7c6e7d5e7e3e8dee8db00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x60c3",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请继续游玩『SD高达G世{00}代DS』吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae9d6e9adea94e9700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83c00e8e7ef96ef9e0de7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x60e7",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也愿你武运长久、奋战不息",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e961e7b8e8ece986ef34e9db02ef46ef28e7b5ec6a000000"
  }
 ]
}
